-><br>and ''[[Sweet Talker (Jessie J album)|Sweet Talker]]''\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| \"[[Love Me Harder]]\"<br /><span style=\"font-size:85%;\">(with [[The Weeknd]])</span>\n| 7 || 19 || 10 || 18 || 17 || \u2014{{efn|\"Love Me Harder\" did not enter the Japan Hot 100, but peaked at number 19 on the Japan Hot Overseas Chart.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.billboard-japan.com/charts/detail?a=d_and_a_overseas&year=2014&month=12&day=1|title=Billboard Japan Hot Overseas|language=Japanese|website=[[Billboard Japan]]|date=December 1, 2014|accessdate=May 8, 2019}}</ref>}} || 12 || 28 || 26 || 48\n|\n* US: 1,300,000<ref name=\"allsales\"/>\n|\n* RIAA: 3\u00d7 Platinum<ref name=\"RIAA\"/>\n* ARIA: 2\u00d7 Platinum<ref name=\"ARIA-sin-2015\"/>\n* BPI: Gold<ref name=\"BPI\"/>\n* FIMI: Platinum<ref name=\"FIMI\"/>\n* GLF: Platinum<ref>{{cite web | url=http://www.sverigetopplistan.se/netdata/ghl002.mbr/artdata?dfom=20140101&sart=4536134| title=Ariana Grande & The Weeknd \u2013 Love Me Harder| publisher=Grammofonleverant\u00f6rernas f\u00f6rening | accessdate=February 10, 2015 | language=Swedish}}</ref>\n* IFPI DEN: Platinum<ref>{{cite web | url=http://www.ifpi.dk/?q=content/ariana-grande-weeknd-love-me-harder-0| title=Ariana Grande and The Weeknd \u2013 Love Me Harder | publisher=IFPI Denmark | accessdate=August 10, 2015 | language=Danish}}</ref>\n* MC: 2\u00d7 Platinum<ref name=\"MC\"/>\n| ''My Everything''\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| \"[[13 (musical)|Brand New You]]\"{{efn-ua|\"Brand New You\" was originally recorded in 2008 when Grande made her acting debut in the [[Broadway theatre|Broadway]] musical show ''[[13 (musical)|13]]''.<ref>{{cite web|title=Ghostlight Records Releases New Ariana Grande Single 'Brand New You' from Jason Robert Brown's 13|url=http://www.broadwayworld.com/article/Ghostlight-Records-Releases-New-Ariana-Grande-Single-Brand-New-You-from-Jason-Robert-Browns-13-20141211|website=Broadwayworld.com|author=BWW News Desk|date=December 11, 2014|accessdate=August 14, 2015}